$ URLs: Text Fragments

A W3C proposal defines a way how to add highlighting and scrolling-to information to a → development/web/URI-URL-URN-IRI-URC#url[URL]. As of this writing (2021-07-05), text fragments
are supported in Version 80 of chromium based → development/web/browser[browsers].

{ Syntax

  The syntax of a text fragment is roughly
code {
https://somehwere.yyy/xyz#:~:text=[prefix-,]textStart[,textEnd][,-suffix]
code }

  The text fragment starts with the `#`.

}
